special_powers.name: SLEP, AS ONE WHO IS DEAD
special_powers.description: Precision Strike. CLOSE/RANGE: Halve damage. Make a close/range attack. Hit characters are given an action token.

special_powers.name: (+5 -OR- +15) BEARER OF THE INFINITY SWORD
special_powers.description: Loki starts the game with any one [ABPI] Infinity Gem equipped. If you paid 15 points, he may instead start with any one [ABPI] Infinity Gauntlet equipped.

special_powers.name: I'LL HAVE THEM CHASING FIGMENTS AND SHADOWS
special_powers.description: Shape Change, Stealth. When Loki uses Shape Change with the ABPI Mind Gem equipped and succeeds, modify the attacking character's combat values -1 until the end of your next turn.

special_powers.name: INFINITY SWORD
special_powers.description: Blades/Claws/Fangs. When Loki uses it and hits, if the attack roll was 10 or higher and the Blades/Claws/Fangs roll was a 5 or 6, after resolutions Action Total +1 this turn and choose a friendly character. Remove all action tokens from the chosen character and that character may be given an additional costed action this turn.

special_powers.name: LAST SURVIVING MEMBER OF THE CORPS
special_powers.description: Captain Britain has PROTECTED: Outwit, but only from characters of less points. When he is damaged by an opponents attack, after resolutions remove an action token from him.

special_powers.name: THE SUN WILL NEVER SET ON BRITANNIA!
special_powers.description: Regeneration, Toughness. Regeneration as FREE, but only if he took damage from an opponent's attack since your last turn.

special_powers.name: INSPIRING PRESENCE AS TIME RUNS OUT
special_powers.description: Empower, Enhancement, Leadership.

special_powers.name: CONTINUITY
special_powers.description: When Kang, The Conqueror is KO'd, at the end of each opposing player's turn, that player rolls a d6. 4-6: That player may remove an action token from one of their characters.

special_powers.name: YOU ARE WATCHING HISTORY BEING MADE!
special_powers.description: FREE: Generate a Time Portal marker in a square within range and line of fire.

special_powers.name: TIME AND TIME AGAIN
special_powers.description: FREE: Place Kang, The Conqueror in an unoccupied square within range that has a Time Portal marker and then heal him 1 click.

special_powers.name: KANG WARS
special_powers.description: X is any number up to the number of unoccupied Time Portal markers on the map. FREE: Place Kang, the Conqueror in an unoccupied square with a Time Portal marker then give him a CLOSE or RANGE action as FREE -or- make an attack. After resolutions, remove that marker. Kang, the Conqueror may be given this FREE action up to X times.

special_powers.name: (+5 -OR- +15) BEARER OF THE INFINITY GAUNTLET
special_powers.description: Rune starts the game with any one [ABPI] Infinity Gem equipped. If you paid 15 points, he may instead start with any one [ABPI] Infinity Gauntlet equipped.

special_powers.name: COSMIC VAMPIRE
special_powers.description: Rune starts the game on click #4. Steal Energy. When Rune uses it, he may heal past his starting line and, if a hit opposing character was 100 points or more or has [Power Cosmic], once per turn he heals an additional click.

special_powers.name: STAR STONES
special_powers.description: Shape Change. Once per attack, he may reroll his Shape Change result of a [2-4].

special_powers.name: (+5 -OR- +15) BEARER OF THE INFINITY GAUNTLET
special_powers.description: The Hood starts the game with any one [ABPI] Infinity Gem equipped. If you paid 15 points, he may instead start with any one [ABPI] Infinity Gauntlet equipped.

special_powers.name: POWER IN THE PALM OF MY HAND
special_powers.description: FREE: If The Hood is equipped with an [ABPaI] Infinity Gem, remove it from the game without scoring it, then equip him with a different [ABPaI] Infinity Gem from outside the game.

special_powers.name: RULE AS THE WORLD BURNS
special_powers.description: When an opposing character rolls for Leadership and the result is [1-2], remove an action token from The Hood.

special_powers.name: INFINITY QUEST
special_powers.description: Phasing/Teleport. When The Hood is equipped with a listed Infinity Gem, he can use the following effects. SPACE: Passenger: 4, but only to carry characters that share a keyword (with him). POWER: When The Hood moves, once per turn after resolutions he may make an attack. REALITY: Stealth. If The Hood or an adjacent character occupy a clear square, lines of fire drawn to them are hindered. // If he's equipped with [ABPaI] Infinity Gauntlet, he can use all of these effects.

special_powers.name: DIMENSIONAL PASSAGE
special_powers.description: Phasing/Teleport. Passenger: 4 and may carry characters with (Wing Symbol). When Lockjaw carries one or more characters and they don't all share a keyword with Lockjaw, after resolutions deal him 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: HE WON'T LET GO!
special_powers.description: Incapacitate. At the end of your turn, if Lockjaw wasn't moved or placed this turn, he can use Incapacitate at no cost.

special_powers.name: INSTINCTIVE JUMP
special_powers.description: STOP. When this click is revealed, after resolutions an opponent must place Lockjaw at least 5 squares away from his current square. When they do, you may place adjacent to Lockjaw all friendly characters that were adjacent to him before being placed.

special_powers.name: MAXIMUS THE MAD!
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, roll a d6. [1-2]: Until your next turn, Maximus can use Battle Fury. [3-4]: Until your next turn, characters within range (including Maximus) can't be given a costed action if they have an action token. [5-6]: Choose an opposing character and a power on their card. That character can't use that power until your next turn.

special_powers.name: MAXIMUS THE MAGNIFICENT!
special_powers.description: Mind Control, Stealth. When Maximus uses Mind Control, after resolutions each hit character is given 2 action tokens.

special_powers.name: MAXIMUS THE MAGNANIMOUS!
special_powers.description: Perplex, but only to target friendly characters. When Maximus uses it, until your next turn, also modify the same combat value +1 on all other friendly characters with the same name as the target.

special_powers.name: JUST BECAUSE YOU HIRED ME, DOESN'T MAKE US FRIENDS
special_powers.description: Taskmaster doesn't count against themed teams

special_powers.name: I MEMORIZED MOVES FROM DOZENS OF CHUMPS, TAKE YOUR BEST SHOT!
special_powers.description: FREE: Choose two: Charge, Flurry, Running Shot, Blades/Claws/Fangs, Incapacitate, Penetrating/Psychic Blast, Precision Strike, Combat Reflexes, Energy Shield/Deflection, Close Combat Expert, Exploit Weakness, Ranged Combat Expert. Taskmaster can use the chosen powers until your next turn. This turn, characters targeted by Taskmaster with an attack can't use the chosen powers until your next turn.

special_powers.name: I SENSE A GREATER CHALLENGE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, if an opponent's force includes an additional game element, heal Challenger 1 click past his starting line to click #0. (Current additional game elements are: ID cards, Equipment, Special Terrain, and Locations.)

special_powers.name: A GAME FOR THE WORLD
special_powers.description: Atthe geginning of the game, you may generate Pyramoid markers anywhere on the map that aren't within 4 squares of each other or a starting area. You generate 3 of them and an opponent generates 2. // When Challenger would take damage, you may instead remove a Pyramoid marker within 6 squares (and take no damage). // Opposing characters have "POWER: Remove from the game a Pyramoid marker in a square this character occupies."

special_powers.name: YOU HAVE SUCCEEDED... IN IRRITATING ME
special_powers.description: STOP. Invincible. FREE: Once per game, make up to 4 attacks (close or range in any combination), each targeting a different opposing character.

special_powers.name: BEARER OF THE POWER GEM
special_powers.description: Champion starts the game with the [ABPI] Power Gem equipped.

special_powers.name: I SENSE A GREATER CHALLENGE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, if an opponent's force includes an additional game element, heal Champion 1 click past his starting line to click #0. (Current additional game elements are: ID cards, Equipment, Special Terrain, and Locations.)

special_powers.name: WHERE'S THE NEXT CHALLENGER?
special_powers.description: Charge. When Champion uses it and hits, after resolutions choose one: Remove an action token from Champion -or- he may make a close attack using Close Combat Expert.

special_powers.name: BEARER OF THE REALITY GEM
special_powers.description: Collector starts the game with the [ABPI] Reality Gem equipped.

special_powers.name: I SENSE A GREATER CHALLENGE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, if an opponent's force includes an additional game element, heal Collector 1 click past his starting line to click #0. (Current additional game elements are: ID cards, Equipment, Special Terrain, and Locations.)

special_powers.name: MY COLLECTION GROWS
special_powers.description: Collector can be equipped with any number of Equipment-Objects at the same time. Protected: Pulse Wave.

special_powers.name: I FIND YOUR HAMMER VERY... UNIQUE
special_powers.description: Incapacitate. When Collector uses it, instead of giving action tokens, after resolutions you may choose one Equipment-Object equipped to a hit character and unequip it. // FREE: Equip an unheld and unequipped opposing Equipment-Object within range and line of fire.

special_powers.name: BEARER OF THE MIND GEM
special_powers.description: Grandmaster starts the game with the [ABPI] Mind Gem equipped.

special_powers.name: I SENSE A GREATER CHALLENGE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, if an opponent's force includes an additional game element, heal Grandmaster 1 click past his starting line to click #0. (Current additional game elements are: ID cards, Equipment, Special Terrain, and Locations.)

special_powers.name: WAGERING ON A CONTEST OF CHAMPIONS, YOU SAY?
special_powers.description: Sidestep. Once per turn, when an opposing character within range and line of fire attacks, before the attack roll you may guess whether or not the attack will hit at least one target. If you do, that attack roll can't be rerolled. If you chose correctly, after resolutions deal the attacking character 1 penetrating damage and heal Grandmaster 1 click. If you're wrong, heal the attacking character 1 click and deal Grandmaster 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: BEARER OF THE SPACE GEM
special_powers.description: Runnerstarts the game with the [ABPI] Space Game equipped

special_powers.name: I SENSE A GREATER CHALLENGE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, if an opponent's force includes an additional game element, heal Runner 1 click past his starting line to click #0. (Current additional game elements are: ID cards, Equipment, Special Terrain, and Locations.)

special_powers.name: GALACTIC MARATHON WINNER
special_powers.description: Hypersonic Speed. FREE: If Runner's printed speed value is the highest on the map, modify his attack or damage +1 until your next turn. If it's at least 3 higher than the next highest, modify both his attack and damage +1 instead.

special_powers.name: CULL OBSIDIAN
special_powers.description: When Ebony Maw is KO'd by an opposing character's attack, after resolutions deal damage to that character equal to the last amount of damage dealt to Ebony Maw. This damage can't be reduced below 1.

special_powers.name: REJOICE AND SURRENDER YOUR LIVES TO THANOS!
special_powers.description: Mind Control, Poison. When Ebony Maw uses Poison, all characters that he has hit with Mind Control this turn are considered to be adjacent (to him).

special_powers.name: PERFECT TELEKINESIS
special_powers.description: Telekinesis. POWER: Choose an unheld object within 6 squares and line of fire. If you do, pick up and hold that object then give Ebony Maw a RANGE Object Action as FREE modifying attack +2 and increasing the damage dealt by +1.

special_powers.name: YOUR POWERS ARE INCONSEQUENTIAL COMPARED TO MINE
special_powers.description: Outwit, Perplex. When Ebony Maw uses either to target an opposing character, once per turn after resolutions you and that opponent each roll a d6. If your result is higher, Ebony Maw may target that same characters with that same power an additional time this turn.

special_powers.name: THE POWER OF THE COSMIC CUBE IS MINE!
special_powers.description: Red Skull starts the game with any one [ABPI] Cosmic Cube equipped.

special_powers.name: THIS "MAN-THING" SHALL HUMBLE YOU
special_powers.description: FREE: Generate an Artificial Being bystander [MAX 1] in a square adjacent to an opposing character attacked Red Skull since your last turn.

special_powers.name: HEAT OF HADES
special_powers.description: Poison, but instead the damage dealt to each opposing character is equal to the number of their action tokens +1.

special_powers.name: RED SKULL, THE MATCHLESS MASTER OF MANKIND
special_powers.description: Leadership, Perplex. When Red Skull uses Leadership and succeeds, he may also remove an action token from an opposing character (anywhere on the map). If he does, this turn Red Skull has "Mind Control as FREE, but only to target that opposing character, regardless of range or line of fire."

special_powers.name: HI, I'M KOBIK
special_powers.description: Kobik starts the game with any one [ABPI] Cosmic Cube equipped.

special_powers.name: REWRITE AFFILIATIONS
special_powers.description: FREE: Choose both a friendly character and an opposing character with printed team abilities. Those characters can use the team abilities printed on the other character instead of their own printed team abilities until your next turn.

special_powers.name: REWRITE HISTORY
special_powers.description: POWER: Once per game, choose an adjacent friendly character on their starting line and a characters on your sideline with the same name as the chosen character. If the first character is equal or more points than the second, replace the first character with the second on their starting line. (That character can't have the same set symbol and collector number.)

special_powers.name: DO YOU WANT TO PLAY?
special_powers.description: Perplex, Probability Control, Shape Change.

special_powers.name: I CAN CREATE A WORLD WITHOUT WAR
special_powers.description: Iron Man starts the game with any one [ABPI] Infinity Gauntlet equipped.

special_powers.name: WISH THE GEMS AND THE GAUNTLET OUT OF EXISTENCE
special_powers.description: When Iron Man would be KO'd, you may KO an equipped [ABPaI] Infinity Gauntlet to turn him to click #6 instead. Protected: Pulse Wave.

special_powers.name: ONLY TO DEFEND EARTH AND OUR REALITY
special_powers.description: Captain America starts the game with any one [ABPI] Infinity Gauntlet equipped.

special_powers.name: THE GEMS... THEY WANT TO BE TOGETHER
special_powers.description: Barrier. Barrier as FREE, but only to generate 1 marker. Captain America can't be healed and takes a maximum of 1 damage from an attack. Protected: Pulse Wave.

special_powers.name: PUSHING PLANETS AWAY
special_powers.description: KNOCKBACK. When Captain America knocks a character back, add 10 to the amount of knock back.

special_powers.name: THE PANTHER GOD
special_powers.description: Stealth. Opposing lines of fire can't be drawn to Black Panther if he occupies printed hindering terrain. Protected: Pulse Wave.

special_powers.name: BEFORE HUMANS TOPPED THE FOOD CHAIN
special_powers.description: Blades/Claws/Fangs. Opposing characters within 3 squares can't use Blades/Claws/Fangs.

special_powers.name: ANCIENT INCARNATION: BLACK PANTHER
special_powers.description: When another friendly character named Black Panther hits, after resolutions remove an action token from this character.

special_powers.name: THE STARBRAND CHOOSES A NEW WIELDER
special_powers.description: When Starbrand is KO'd, after resolutions roll a d6 for each character (friendly and opposing) within 6 squares of the square he last occupied. The character with the highest result modifies its combat values +1 this game. (Reroll the highest ties until only one character has the highest result.) Protected: Pulse Wave.

special_powers.name: BEFORE INTERSTELLAR TRAVEL
special_powers.description: Starbrand and friendly characters within 3 squares can't be attacked by opposing characters using Hypersonic Speed.

special_powers.name: ANCIENT INCARNATION: STARBRAND
special_powers.description: When another friendly character named Starbrand hits, after resolutions remove an action token from this character.

special_powers.name: ARTIFACT FROM THE INTER-DIMENSIONAL COSMIC VAMPIRE
special_powers.description: Thanos may start the game with the [ABPaI] Ego Gem equipped.

special_powers.name: SKREET IS AS SKREET DOES, AND SKREET IS HARD TO SWAT
special_powers.description: FREE:  Once per game, generate a Skreet bystander.

special_powers.name: GENOCIDE IS NOT WHAT MISTRESS DEATH DESIRES, BUT IT'S WHAT THE MAKER'S FOLLOWERS DESERVE
special_powers.description: Precision Strike. FREE: Make an attack targeting an opposing character, but only if there's another opposing character with the same name on the map. // When Thanos KO's a character, after resolutions KO all bystanders generated by that character, then heal him 1 click for each bystander KO'd this way.

special_powers.name: THE BIOLOGICAL APPLICATION OF COSMIC POWER
special_powers.description: Perplex, but only to target other characters. When Thanos uses it to target a friendly character, that character can use [Power Cosmic] until your next turn. When Thanos uses it to target an opposing character, that character can't use Willpower or PROTECTED: Outwit or Protected: Outwit until your next turn.

special_powers.name: CHAOS MITE
special_powers.description: Perplex, but only to target other characters. When Skreet uses it, she modifies a value +2 or -2 instead, then rolls a d6. [1-2]: The modifier becomes 0 instead.

special_powers.name: CYBERNETIC ARM
special_powers.description: Close Combat Expert. Super Senses, but only succeeds on a [6].

special_powers.name: ELIMINATING TARGETS
special_powers.description: Ranged Combat Expert. RANGE: Make up to two range attacks.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: This character gains an extra target. Perplex, Telekinesis. // When this character hits, if the attack roll was 10 or higher, after resolutions they may generate an object to immediately hold. If you do, give them a RANGE Object Action as FREE. If they continue to hit with an attack roll of 10 or higher, they may use this effect an additional time.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: Modify range +1. Probability Control. When this character attacks, if the attack roll is 10 or higher, opposing characters can't use effects to reroll attacks this turn.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: Modify damage +1. Close Combat Expert, Range Combat Expert. When this character hits, if the attack roll was 10 or higher, after resolutions deal a hit target 1 penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: Modify speed +1. Phasing/Teleport, Passenger: 2. When this character hits, if the attack roll was 10 or higher, after resolutions you may place a hit character up to 8 squares away from their current square.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: Modify defense +1. Steal energy, but with close or range attacks. When this character hits, if the attack roll was 10 or higher, after resolutions heal 1 click.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: Modify attack +1. Mind Control, Incapacitate. // When this character hits, if the attack roll was 10 or higher, after resolutions they can use Mind Control as FREE. If they continue to hit with an attack roll of 10 or higher, they may use this effect an additional time.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: FREE: An opponent chooses Speed, Attack, Defense, or Damage and you then choose a standard power that isn't of the chosen type. Until your next turn, as long as the Cosmic Cube is equipped, modify the combat value of the type chosen by your opponent +1 and this character can use the power you chose. At the end of your turn, roll a d6 if this character doesn't have the Cosmic keyword. [1-2]: Unequip the Cosmic Cube.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: FREE: Choose one: Place this character up to 3 squares away from its current square; -or- Until your next turn, [Improved Targeting: Elevated, Hindering] and modify range +2; -or- Give an action token to an adjacent opposing character. If you can't, deal them 1 penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: FREE: Choose a standard power, then roll a d6. [5-6]: You may choose an additional standard power. [1-2]: Deal this character 1 unavoidable damage. This character can use the chosen power(s) until your next turn.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: Infinity Gauntlet starts with 6 Infinity tokens. [Power Cosmic].

special_powers.name: FREE
special_powers.description: Choose standard powers from this list up to the number of Infinity tokens: Mind Control, Pulse Wave, Close Combat Expert, Ranged Combat Expert, opposing Probability Control, and Poison. Until your next turn, this character has PROTECTED from all of the chosen powers. After resolutions, roll a d6. [2-4] Remove an Infinity token. [1]: Remove an Infinity token and deal this character 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: This character can be equipped with any number of [ABPaI] Infinity Gems with different names. FREE: Choose a combat value to modify +1 until your next turn.
